1
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,000
Driver, do you remember the way?

2
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,170
Don't worry,

3
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,440
Mr. Fang has already given instructions.

4
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:02,880
Good.

5
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,120
Mom.

6
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,240
Stop wiping,

7
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,770
I've already wiped it once.

8
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:01,640
It looks like cat scratches,

9
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,360
not clean.

10
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,920
That's enough.

11
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,200
The kids who come here to dance,

12
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,480
it's not just about how well they dance,

13
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,760
it's mainly about

14
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:16,490
how they feel watching themselves in the mirror.

15
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,360
You must be exhausted doing this every day.

16
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,640
What's going on?

17
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,890
Are you leaving?

18
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,700
Yeah, I'm leaving.

19
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,640
So early?

20
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,480
Why not stay for lunch?

21
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,280
No, I'll pass.

22
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,840
Waiting here

23
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,880
or at the airport,

24
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,880
it's all the same.

25
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,720
You just can't sit still,

26
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,490
why not send Xiaoyao a message?

27
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,120
I did.

28
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,329
What did she say?

29
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,320
She didn't reply.

30
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,640
Then call her.

31
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,480
Tell her you're going on a business trip.

32
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:52,000
Even if you can't be friends, you can still be acquaintances.

33
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,480
Really, there's no need.

34
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,040
I sent the message like you suggested,

35
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,120
and she didn't reply,

36
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,800
which

37
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,620
is actually a reply in itself.

38
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,720
Besides, we had an agreement.

39
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,880
I'd accompany her

40
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:03,880
to experience life

41
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,520
and practice until the performance day,

42
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,680
which is today.

43
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,680
As a grown man,

44
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,000
if I keep pestering her,

45
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,360
it would be embarrassing

46
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,280
and annoying.

47
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,440
Besides, she must be busy with her premiere today.

48
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,339
You're quite considerate of others.

49
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,329
I'm leaving.

50
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,480
Let me walk you out.

51
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,240
No need,

52
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,880
mom will see you off.

53
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,480
You never offered to walk me out before,

54
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,410
so I'll just leave like this today,

55
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,520
don't bother.

56
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,380
Go back inside.

57
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,159
You can go.

58
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,080
Go back in.

59
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,400
Did you bring your ID card?

60
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,130
Credit card?

61
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,480
It's not my first time leaving.

62
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,560
You never asked all these details

63
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,040
when I left before.

64
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,480
You're acting like we'll never see each other again,

65
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,610
but I'm coming back.

66
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,760
How long will you be gone this time?

67
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,890
About ten days or so.

68
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:56,970
Text me when you arrive.

69
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,050
Don't worry,

70
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,640
I'll take pictures for you.

71
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,960
You didn't take photos of the square dancing

72
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,840
yesterday.

73
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,820
I'll take them when I get back.

74
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:05,400
You know,

75
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:07,400
you should really try square dancing sometime,

76
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,660
it's very refreshing.

77
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,080
I'd rather die than do that.

78
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,170
Don't say such unlucky things,

79
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,900
spit it out!

80
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,320
Where's Xier?

81
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,180
I don't see her.

82
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:20,880
Tell her for me

83
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,740
that I've left.

84
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,330
Go ahead.

85
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,280
Just between us,

86
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,240
she's having a hard time,

87
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,370
so stop pressuring her about the rent.

88
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,330
What do you mean?

89
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,720
It's been so long,

90
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,240
she'll pay us when she has money.

91
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,360
She's not that kind of person.

92
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,720
Her life is hard enough already,

93
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:39,320
if you keep pushing her for rent, how can she survive?

94
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,380
Alright, alright.

95
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,159
Let's go.

96
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:42,900
I'm off now.

97
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,570
Are you walking to the airport?

98
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,760
I called a car.

99
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,560
It's waiting for me at the corner.

100
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,360
Let's go back.

101
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,640
Let's go in.

102
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,250
When I see him later,

103
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,370
I don't know what to say.

104
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,140
Let him do the talking.

105
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,690
He's nervous about seeing you too.

106
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:31,720
Really?

107
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,680
Clear your mind,

108
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,920
empty your thoughts,

109
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,520
let your brain reach

110
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,970
a state of tranquility.

111
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,200
Only then will your spirit

112
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:42,960
and body

113
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,600
completely

114
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,760
rest.

115
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,440
Xiaomi.

116
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,080
Xiaomi,

117
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,000
could you get my phone for me?

118
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,800
Yaoyao and Yin Ye

119
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,640
have the most selfish thoughts.

120
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:24,680
Qiaomi

121
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:26,680
is the most innocent.

122
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,010
So I'm just stupid, huh?

123
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,520
Having selfish thoughts

124
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,780
doesn't mean it's bad.

125
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,440
Being innocent isn't wrong either.

126
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,840
Human emotions and desires

127
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,520
are the roots of artistic expression. Don't be trapped by them.

128
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:41,250
You sure can spin words around.

129
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,200
Do you want to get off?

130
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,340
No need.

131
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,840
I'll ask Zhou Tong to come over this afternoon.

132
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,680
You're

133
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,160
so busy this afternoon.

134
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,340
I get anxious when I don't see him.

135
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:19,880
I was

136
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,360
going to make up with him.

137
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,930
But his attitude was terrible.

138
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:24,840
Xiaomi

139
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:25,660
is here.

140
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,880
Go do whatever you need to do,

141
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:29,940
stop clinging to Yaoyao all the time.

142
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,360
Getting all high and mighty now,

143
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,400
forgetting who helped you when I'm also a lead actor.

144
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,760
You're not doing interviews anyway,

145
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,620
go take a break.

146
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,460
Yaoyao.

147
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,400
Yaoyao,

148
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,200
hurry up.

149
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,039
Coming!

150
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,680
Thank you everyone for your hard work.

151
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,360
So.

152
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,240
Let's...

153
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,200
In 15 minutes,

154
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,000
she hasn't eaten yet,

155
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,800
in 15 minutes,

156
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,640
one at a time,

157
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,720
finish before 4 o'clock.

158
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,420
Yaoyao.

159
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,120
The food is on the table,

160
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,560
go help yourself.

161
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,280
Calm down.

162
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,240
Calm down.

163
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:06,760
Look, look!

164
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:07,720
She's coming out!

165
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,800
Miss Wen is coming out!

166
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,040
Miss Wen, may we have an interview?

167
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,280
Can we have an interview?

168
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,680
What's wrong, Mom?

169
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:09,120
Are you at the airport yet?

170
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,920
Almost there.

171
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,570
Why is it taking so long?

172
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:13,040
There's a bit of traffic.

173
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,320
I never used to care

174
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,580
where you went before.

175
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,520
You went to Malaysia?

176
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:29,880
Yes,

177
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,320
where else would I go?

178
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:35,080
You didn't go looking for Xiao Yao, did you?

179
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,280
If I wanted to see her,

180
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:39,000
would I need to buy a plane ticket? Think about it.

181
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,800
I'm feeling so anxious about this.

182
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,680
Something's definitely

183
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,560
fishy here.

184
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:44,320
Actually,

185
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:45,200
I just went

186
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,400
to see Xiao Yao.

187
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,040
Are you with her now?

188
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,600
I texted her but she didn't respond.

189
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,000
If that's the case,

190
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,210
just come back home.

191
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,700
If you can't let go,

192
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,960
how can you leave?

193
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,800
I really can't let go, Mom.

194
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,880
What should I do?

195
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:02,840
I feel miserable.

196
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:04,920
She's a nice girl.

197
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,880
You two have history together.

198
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,480
Come back

199
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:08,620
and start over.

200
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:10,760
Go back?

201
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,720
I'm already at the airport.

202
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,320
Who are you kidding?

203
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,120
In this state,

204
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,050
you can't leave.

205
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:19,010
So I'm really coming back then.

206
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:19,800
Come home.

207
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:22,210
I'll feel better when you're back.

208
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,120
Gotta go,

209
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,380
getting out of the car.

210
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,880
I care about you

211
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,300
so I'll waive your rent

212
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,160
for two months

213
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,460
but not for half a year.

214
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:38,680
Really?

215
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,600
Three months.

216
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,340
You're so kind.

217
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,440
Brother Tong.

218
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,250
Want me to keep you company?

219
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,900
You're just trying to fool me.

220
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,760
So this is where we get off?

221
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,730
You're lying through your teeth to me!

222
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:03,740
Alright, alright,

223
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,600
come on in,

224
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,220
let's go upstairs.

225
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,940
Where's your luggage?

226
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,400
Well...

227
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,330
What do you mean?

228
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,560
Don't tell me you're looking for Xiaoyao?

229
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,400
Hello, ma'am.

230
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:20,440
And you are?

231
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:21,920
Hello, ma'am.

232
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,240
My name is Xu Tian,

233
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,540
I'm from Hangzhou.

234
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:25,720
We're here

235
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,060
to visit Zhou Tong.

236
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,060
This is my girlfriend,

237
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,880
Shi Diandian.

238
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,000
Hello, ma'am.

239
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:04,880
Okay.

240
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:06,320
We'll be going now.

241
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,920
That woman just now was Zhou Tong's mother.

242
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,400
Zhou Tong isn't here,

243
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,530
he went to Malaysia.

244
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,320
What were you

245
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,850
talking about just now?

246
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,040
About you.

247
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:27,730
Let's go.

248
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:29,660
I'm coming.

249
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,400
He's not here.

250
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:32,410
Let's go.

251
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,280
Get in the car.

252
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:57,690
Wait, open the door.

253
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:04,760
Ma'am.

254
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,440
You look so alike.

255
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,680
I'm Song Guanwang.

256
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,650
I'm Zhou Tong's mother.

257
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,040
You've come from so far away.

258
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:21,720
Come,

259
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,980
come in and have a seat.

260
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,850
I'll wait for you in the car.

261
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,770
I'm already at the airport,

262
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,360
heading to Malaysia.

263
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:51,170
Thank you for giving me these six days,

264
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:52,810
I really took it seriously.

265
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,560
Even a complete fool

266
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,720
would truly like you.

267
00:15:57,920 --> 00:15:59,320
Good luck with your White Snake performance.

268
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,980
Wen Xiaoyao, can we start now?

269
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,200
Just stay seated,

270
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,260
look at the camera.

271
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,480
I'm sorry,

272
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,450
my stuff is here.

273
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:40,760
I didn't mean anything by it.

274
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:41,290
Xiaoyao,

275
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:43,410
these things belong to Sister Yun.

276
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:01,600
You big fool.

277
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:03,400
The video Xiaomi showed you

278
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:04,930
was just me comforting her.

279
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:05,970
Without you,

280
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:07,740
there would be no White Snake.

281
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:10,260
Did you forget what we said on the Great Wall?

282
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,319
I love you.

283
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:11,920
Are you coming or not?

284
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:12,720
Zhou Tong.

285
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,960
Can we begin now?

286
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:24,160
I need to make a video call first,

287
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:26,359
I'll just leave it aside without talking.

288
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,089
That's fine.

289
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:38,080
How do you

290
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:41,280
interpret this version of White Snake in the dance drama?

291
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:45,050
I've never been in love before.

292
00:17:45,560 --> 00:17:47,360
Because of dancing White Snake,

293
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:48,360
I met someone

294
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:49,930
named Zhou Tong.

295
