00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,880
look here, look here.

590
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,080
Fine, I'm not taking photos.

591
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:30,980
Yaoyao,

592
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:33,160
I've told you everything you need to know.

593
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,360
You have five minutes

594
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:35,120
before closing the doors to visitors.

595
00:28:35,120 --> 00:28:36,580
Am I considered a visitor?

596
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,480
I am a visitor.

597
00:28:38,840 --> 00:28:40,040
I'm sorry, Director.

598
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,120
The pressure is too much,

599
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,840
let's cut him some slack.

600
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:48,800
Uncle Hui,

601
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,520
could you help me at the entrance later

602
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:51,280
to wait for Zhou Tong

603
00:28:51,280 --> 00:28:52,480
and give him a ticket?

604
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,280
You still want to give him a ticket?

605
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,810
I haven't given him one yet.

606
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,820
I have one here,

607
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,280
let's take a photo first.

608
00:28:58,280 --> 00:28:58,610
Okay.

609
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:02,680
Let's go.

610
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:04,520
Everyone's here.

611
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:05,400
Don't be nervous,

612
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,730
I'll go to the entrance.

613
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,320
Come on!

614
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:15,680
Really?

615
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:17,720
Zhou Butong is actually coming?

616
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,250
He was heading to Malaysia,

617
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:21,400
but now he's on his way back from the airport.

618
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:23,000
So you two worked things out?

619
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,800
What did you say to each other?

620
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:27,800
I asked him to come back and he did.

621
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:33,810
Zhou Butong didn't say anything bad about me, did he?

622
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,370
He spoke well of you.

623
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:39,570
That's good,

624
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,600
so what happens next?

625
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,520
I guess I'm his now.

626
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,040
How can you be his person?

627
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:45,840
What about me?

628
00:29:45,840 --> 00:29:46,440
I'm still yours.

629
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,770
He belongs to both of us,

630
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:48,730
he's our person.

631
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:51,280
So I should call him brother-in-law now, right?

632
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:52,010
Pretty much.

633
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,200
Then I'll treat him like Xu Xian,

634
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,120
waiting for him to make mistakes.

635
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:57,520
Help me keep an eye on him,

636
00:29:59,160 --> 00:29:59,690
go on now.

637
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,540
Going to put on makeup.

638
00:30:04,360 --> 00:30:05,220
Close the door.

639
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,240
Oh my God,

640
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:26,200
is heaven trying to destroy me?

641
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:28,520
To get to Hufang Bridge,

642
00:30:28,520 --> 00:30:29,840
it'll be 7 o'clock at least,

643
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:31,970
walking would be faster than driving.

644
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,240
No way.

645
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:35,680
Driver,

646
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,760
I'm getting out.

647
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,040
You're really leaving?

648
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,920
I can't afford to waste time like this.

649
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:40,880
I'll take the subway,

650
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,640
alternating between riding and running would be much better.

651
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:44,000
What's so urgent?

652
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,530
Another blind date.

653
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:48,400
Thank you.

654
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,640
Please leave a good review.

655
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,300
Sure thing.

656
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,210
Can you handle food this spicy?

657
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,010
A little bit is fine.

658
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:15,370
Then let's look at something else.

659
00:31:17,320 --> 00:31:18,380
Jiangzhe cuisine.

660
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:21,280
You come to Beijing just once

661
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:23,340
and you want to eat Jiangzhe cuisine?

662
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,060
I won't come again.

663
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,700
We won't go anywhere else after this.

664
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:31,000
We'll go back to Hangzhou,

665
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:31,960
you'll go to work,

666
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,160
and I'll make qipaos.

667
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,080
What if I don't work?

668
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,200
I can support you.

669
00:31:41,840 --> 00:31:43,170
Roast duck! Roast duck!

670
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:46,530
There's a four-star restaurant here.

671
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:49,160
Aren't we inviting your mother?

672
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:51,210
Let's eat by ourselves.

673
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:52,640
Okay.

674
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,500
I've warmed up.

675
00:31:57,840 --> 00:31:59,640
Hui is waiting for you at the ballet company entrance,

676
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,360
and asks Mrs. Song to come watch the performance too.

677
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:02,360
I'm on the subway,

678
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:03,160
be there soon.

679
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,360
Is it far?

680
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:51,800
Not far,

681
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,280
just past that traffic light ahead,

682
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,040
turn left,

683
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,800
then right, then left again.

684
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,440
I don't want to hear all that,

685
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:00,640
I'll just follow you.

686
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,100
Don't need your ears anymore?

687
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:06,440
I don't even need my eyes.

688
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:09,370
Aren't you afraid of losing me?

689
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,360
This way I won't lose you.

690
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:20,960
Then close your eyes.

691
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,480
Please don't walk too fast.

692
00:33:43,080 --> 00:33:43,760
No peeking.

693
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:46,280
I'm not.

694
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,810
I'll blindfold you.

695
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:53,000
Emergency! Excuse me! Coming through!

696
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,060
Thank you! Thanks!

697
00:33:54,280 --> 00:33:55,280
Thank you so much!

698
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,000
Coming! Almost there, Xiaoyao!

699
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,400
I'm out of the subway now.

700
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,320
Mom.

701
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,250
Go ahead.

702
00:34:31,719 --> 00:34:33,000
I didn't hear my phone.

703
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:34,960
The children are here for class.

704
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:36,659
Why are you panting like that?

705
00:34:37,159 --> 00:34:37,960
It's nothing,

706
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:38,719
um,

707
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:39,920
later,

708
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:41,920
we're going to see Xiaoyao's performance,

709
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,960
Mr. Qiao is waiting for us at the ballet company entrance.

710
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,620
Mr. Qiao again? I'm not going.

711
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,320
You're just telling me now?

712
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:47,760
Son.

713
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,440
What's wrong?

714
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:50,760
Let me tell you,

715
00:34:51,159 --> 00:34:52,889
today, shortly after you left,

716
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:53,840
someone from Hangzhou

717
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,560
named Xu Tian came by,

718
00:34:56,080 --> 00:34:57,610
who looks exactly like you,

719
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,520
and I mistook him for you.

720
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:02,600
A southerner

721
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:04,290
who talks all fancy.

722
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:06,320
When it was raining in Hangzhou,

723
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,320
you changed clothes at his shop.

724
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,040
Remember?

725
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:12,560
He actually

726
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,820
came to Beijing specifically to see you.

727
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:16,680
After chatting with me for a while,

728
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:17,240
he said

729
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,680
he's going back home to live a quiet life

730
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:20,140
and won't come back again.

731
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,330
You're not saying anything again.

732
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,890
Look, I don't have time to go there.

733
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,160
Diandian.

734
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,020
What's wrong with you?

735
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:33,100
What happened?

736
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,840
Just had a car accident

737
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:37,770
and hit someone.

738
00:36:38,600 --> 00:36:39,560
Did you see it?

739
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:11,920
Is there

740
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:13,720
roast duck here?

741
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:16,440
No.

742
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,360
Don't be afraid,

743
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:20,960
it's okay.

744
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,480
Was that person

745
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,080
badly hurt in the collision?

746
00:37:24,120 --> 00:37:24,850
I don't know.

747
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:32,850
Wait for me here.

748
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:34,330
Where are you going?

749
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,080
Bathroom.

750
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:36,900
Then I'll order first.

751
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,460
Wait for me right here.

752
00:38:40,040 --> 00:38:41,370
What are you doing here?

753
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,450
Are you his girlfriend?

754
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:18,960
Phone.

755
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:32,180
Hello, son.

756
00:39:32,200 --> 00:39:34,000
Have you arrived at the theater?

757
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,840
Ever since you left today,

758
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,370
I've been feeling anxious.

759
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,650
What's so special about today?

760
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:41,680
Have you seen Xiaoyao?

761
00:39:48,200 --> 00:39:48,860
Who is this?

762
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,740
Why are you crying?

763
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,120
Ma'am,

764
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:55,120
it's Diandian.

765
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:57,160
Diandian?

766
00:39:58,040 --> 00:39:59,560
Are you with Zhou Tong?

767
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,960
We're going to the hospital,

768
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,520
Zhou Tong was hit by a car.

769
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:22,850
Are you nervous?

770
00:41:23,640 --> 00:41:24,480
Not at all.

771
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,250
I'm a little bit.

772
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,720
Zhou Tong should be downstairs already, right?

773
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:30,480
Definitely.

774
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,600
Love you, Xiaomi.

775
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:34,280
Me too.

776
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,180
Just watching.

777
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:03,180
You finally answered your phone.

778
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,720
Is Zhou Tong with you?

779
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:07,490
The show started over half an hour ago.

780
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,570
I'll be right there.

781
00:43:16,440 --> 00:43:17,500
Styling Assistant

782
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,880
Hair Styling Lead Assistant

783
00:43:38,200 --> 00:43:38,930
Wang Jianfei

784
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:49,370
Project Manager

785
00:43:55,160 --> 00:43:55,320
Project Producer
